 upon you.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6529 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari Ibn al-Qayyim said, \u201cSome of the scholars said it\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43070,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/03\/13\/youth-greeting-adults\/","url_meta":{"origin":43066,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salaam: Youth greeting adults with peace","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 13, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe young should greet elders with peace, the passerby should greet those sitting, and the small group should greet the large group.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6233 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11575,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/22\/greeting-visit-qabr-madinah\/","url_meta":{"origin":43066,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Ziyarah: Greeting the Prophet at his grave","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 22, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNone of you greets me with peace (at his grave) except Allah returns my spirit, that I may return his greeting of peace.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 2041 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Nawawi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15409,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/28\/allah-teaches-adam-salaam\/","url_meta":{"origin":43066,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salaam: Allah teaches Adam greeting of peace","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 28, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah created Adam in His image, sixty cubits tall. When He created him, Allah said: Go and greet these groups of assembled angels with peace and listen to how they greet you, for this will be the greeting\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32028,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/14\/prophet-fears-sins-tongue\/","url_meta":{"origin":43066,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Speech: The Prophet fears sins of the tongue","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 14, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Sufyan ibn 'Abdillah reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, tell me of a matter I can depend upon?\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSay: My Lord is Allah. Then, remain upright.\u201d I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what do you fear most for\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15427,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/28\/etiquette-adab-spread-peace\/","url_meta":{"origin":43066,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Salaam: Greeting groups with peace","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 28, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe rider should greet with peace those who are walking, those who are walking should greet those who are sitting, and a small group should greet a larger group.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6232, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2160\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/43066","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=43066"}],"version-history"